data.name: lblHowToPlay.Text
data.value:
Squirrel Bob's quest for the Chestnut.
In this game you need to carefully move your mouse cursor through the maze.
Goal of the game is to get Squirrel Bob to the chestnut.
In the maze there is also a treasure. Find out what it does.
If you right click before starting to move the cursor will show your path with a line.
There is an easy and a hard mode.
How many tries does it take you to help Bob out? and if all else fails are you able to cheat your way to the chestnut?
